### Get Prompt by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/prompts/1
Content-Type: application/json

### Create Prompt
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/prompts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "promptNumber": "TEST102",
  "prompt": "This is a test prompt."
}

### Update Prompt
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/prompts/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "promptNumber": "TEST101",
  "prompt": "This is a test prompt - updated."
}
